Title: agent_aws: Support for Assume Role
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1572863256
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

AWS Assume Role let you access resources from another account. This feature enables CheckMK to monitor resources from another AWS account without an explicit monitoring user.
For more information please see the AWS documentation. 
